        * DICOM Standard, Part 4, :dcm:`Annex H <part04/chapter_H.html>`
        * DICOM Standard, Part 4, :dcm:`Annex S <part04/chapter_S.html>`
        * DICOM Standard, Part 4, :dcm:`Annex CC <part04/chapter_CC.html>`
